window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cornell is broken after losing his best friend Jonas and getting hurt himself. He’s too old, too imperfect to ever attract a Dom again.</p> <p>Until Rhys.</p> <p>When Rhys gives him commands, Cornell yearns to obey.</p> <p>When Rhys takes care of him, Cornell wants to kneel for him. When Rhys is everything he’s dreamed of, Cornell aches to call him Sir. And when Rhys makes him fly, Cornell soars higher than ever before.</p> <p>But there’s one problem. Rhys is 20 years old and is a junior...and he’s Jonas’s son. How can you want to call your best friend’s son \"Sir\"...or \"Daddy\"?</p> <p><i>Firm Hand </i>is a standalone slow burn MM romance with daddy kink, an age gap, a very caring Daddy, and a boy who needs it, hurt/comfort, mild D/s play, and all the feels.</p>"; 
